4. In your activity or fragment where you want to retrieve the data, create a method to read the txt file and parse its content into a list of Book objects. For example:

```java
private List<Book> readTxtFile() {
    List<Book> books = new ArrayList<>();
    try {
        InputStream inputStream = getAssets().open("books.txt");
        BufferedReader reader = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(inputStream));
        String line;
        while ((line = reader.readLine()) != null) {
            String[] parts = line.split(",");
